00:55:32,695 --> 00:55:37,045
how much l am in the favour of Margaret,
the waiting gentlewoman to Hero.

734
00:55:37,300 --> 00:55:40,950
- I remember.
- I can, at any unseasonable instant of the night. . .

735
00:55:41,204 --> 00:55:43,754
appoint her to look out
at her lady's chamber window.

736
00:55:44,074 --> 00:55:46,224
What life is in that
to be the death of this marriage ?

737
00:55:46,476 --> 00:55:49,076
The poison of that
lies in you to temper.

738
00:56:20,175 --> 00:56:21,175
Gallants. . .

739
00:56:21,844 --> 00:56:24,844
I am not as l have been.

